#. type: <p></p>
#: maint-guide.en.sgml:2567 maint-guide.en.sgml:2666
msgid ""
"create and sign the upload <file>.changes</file> file, using "
"<prgn>dpkg-genchanges</prgn> and <prgn>gpg</prgn>"
